227
00:22:23.632 --> 00:22:25.965
Je hebt gekletst over Mars!

228
00:22:26.132 --> 00:22:29.132
Ben je gek geworden?
Ik weet niks over Mars!


229
00:22:29.590 --> 00:22:33.757
